17 inherited metabolic and genetic disorders as identified by the department. The department
18 shall be authorized to consider recommendations from the Newborn Screening and
19 Genetics Advisory Committee established pursuant to subsection (i) of this Code section,
20 to include disorders which are added to the federal Recommended Uniform Screening
21 Panel and may be identified in the future to result in serious illness, severe physical or
22 developmental disability, and death if undiagnosed and untreated."
23 SECTION 2.
24 This Act shall become effective on January 1, 2026.
25 SECTION 3.
26 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
